me.unei.lang.api

Class Language

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.unei.lang.api.Language

  • public final class Language
extends Object
    Represents a single and unique language (eg: English US 'en_US')

    To get one see LanguageManager.getLanguage(String).

      • get

        public final String get(String key)
        Gets a translated text for a given key or return the key itself if none available.

        It is the same as calling "get(key, key)".

        Parameters:
        key - The translation key.
        Returns:
        Returns the translated text for the key (or 'key' if none available).
